2020年8月23日晚17时，美国非裔男子'''雅各布·布莱克'''（{{lang-en|Jacob Blake}}）与警方发生冲突，导致前者中枪并[[瘫痪|瘫痪]]。事发之时，[[基诺沙_(威斯康辛州)|威斯康辛州基诺沙市]]警方正因[[家庭暴力|家庭暴力]]问题意图逮捕布莱克，而布莱克则径直走向自己的车，在侧身进入驾驶室中时被警员拉斯滕·谢斯基（Rusten Sheskey）从后背连开7枪。<ref>{{cite web |title=美國威斯康辛州警員「連開七槍」射傷黑人，再次引發多處暴力抗議 |url=https://bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-53931406 |website=BBC News 中文 |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2020-08-27 |language=zh-Hant |date=2020-08-27}}</ref>此次枪击事件引发了美国社会的巨大反响，在基诺沙市亦引发了一系列市民[[基诺沙暴乱|抗议、毁坏财产、放火]]等一系列事件，并成为[[Black_Lives_Matter|Black Lives Matter]]运动中的一部分。<ref name=PeiserWP>{{Cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/nation/2020/08/23/kenosha-police-shooting-video-wisconsin/|title=After video shows Wisconsin police shooting a Black man multiple times, National Guard is called to Kenosha|first1=Jaclyn|last1=Peiser|first2=Mark|last2=Berman|first3=Mark|last3=Guarino|first4=Paulina|last4=Firozi|first5=Griff|last5=Witte|work=Washington Post|date=2020-08-24|accessdate=August 26, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200825040228/https://www.washingtonpost.com/nation/2020/08/23/kenosha-police-shooting-video-wisconsin/|archivedate=2020-08-25}}</ref>

==事发==
[[File:2805_40th_St_Kenosha_WI.jpg|thumb]]
8月23日17:11时，基诺沙警方接到一通关于“家庭问题”的911报警。据多份官方警情通报，女报警人将布莱克呼作其男友，称其擅闯住宅，抢走了她的车钥匙不放。<ref name="Chavez">{{Cite web|last=Chavez|first=Nicole|title=What we know so far about Jacob Blake's shooting|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/08/27/us/jacob-blake-shooting-what-we-know/index.html|access-date=2020-08-31|website=CNN}}</ref><ref name="Freiman">{{cite news | last1 = Freiman | first1 = Jordan| last2 = Carissimo | first2 = Justin | date = 2020-08-25 | title = Police in Wisconsin Shoot Black Man in Back Multiple Times, Sparking Protests | url = https://www.cbsnews.com/news/jacob-blake-kenosha-shooting-wisconsin-police-black-man-protesters-gather/ | work = [[CBS_News|CBS News]]}}</ref>[[签派员|签派员]]亦用警情代码“10-99”通知基诺沙警方该地可能有“通缉犯”。<ref name="NRVerBruggen1" />布莱克当时被控三级[[性骚扰|性骚扰]]、擅闯侵权、因[[家庭暴力|家庭暴力]]妨害治安，警方有对他的[[逮捕令|逮捕令]]。<ref name= "JSJones1">{{cite news |last1=Jones |first1=Meg |last2=Taschler |first2=Joe |title=Less than 3 minutes passed between when Kenosha police arrived and when Jacob Blake was shot, according to dispatch audio |url=https://www.jsonline.com/story/news/2020/08/25/kenosha-police-shot-jacob-blake-3-minutes-after-arrival-audio-reveals/5628076002/ |accessdate=2020-08-28 |agency=''[[Milwaukee_Journal_Sentinel|Milwaukee Journal Sentinel]]'' |date=2020-08-25|publisher=[[Gannett_Company|Gannett Company]]}}</ref><ref name="NRVerBruggen1">{{cite news |last1=VerBruggen |first1=Robert |title=What We Know about the Jacob Blake Shooting |url=https://www.nationalreview.com/2020/08/what-we-know-about-the-jacob-blake-shooting/ |accessdate=2020-08-27 |work=[[National_Review|National Review]] |date=2020-08-27}}</ref>拨打911报警的女报警人便是此前指控布莱克性骚扰她的人。<ref name="Eligon">{{Cite news|last=Eligon|first=John|last2=Mervosh|first2=Sarah|last3=Jr|first3=Richard A. Oppel|date=2020-08-28|title=Jacob Blake Was Shackled in Hospital Bed After Police Shot Him|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/28/us/jacob-blake-shackles-assault.html|access-date=2020-08-30|issn=0362-4331}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-26|title=Jacob Blake Criminal Complaint For Third Degree Sexual Assault ||url=http://archive.is/YcYRU|access-date=2020-08-30 |website=[[Scribd|Scribd]]}}</ref>基诺沙警长Daniel Miskinis和基诺沙警察行业协会（Kenosha Professional Police Association）均称，警察在23日出警时就已经知晓对布莱克的逮捕令。<ref name="Eligon"/><ref name="Graymedia">{{cite news |title=Police association: Jacob Blake physically struggled with officers before shooting |url=https://www.wbay.com/2020/08/28/jacob-blake-no-longer-in-restraints-in-hospital-more-kenosha-officers-identified/ |accessdate=2020-08-30 |location=Green Bay |website=[[WBAY-TV|WBAY-TV]] |publisher=[[Gray_Television|Gray Television]] |date=2020-08-28}}</ref><ref name="APKARE">{{cite news |last1=Richmond |first1=Todd |title=Kenosha police union gives its version of Jacob Blake shooting |url=https://www.kare11.com/article/news/nation-world/kenosha-police-union-gives-its-version-of-jacob-blake-shooting/507-90ab65b9-8e04-4283-aa07-ba141925928f |accessdate=2020-08-30 |agency=Associated Press |website=KARE-TV |date=2020-08-28}}</ref>

一名证人称，布莱克将车开到了“有六七名女子在路边互相大喊大叫”的地方，“布莱克一句话都没对她们说”。<ref>{{cite news | date = 2020-08-24 | last1 = Householder | first1 = Mike | last2 = Webber | first2 = Tammy | title = Kenosha, Wisconsin Shooting: Police Shoot Black Man From Behind; Protests Erupt With State Of Emergency Declared | url = https://abc7news.com/protest-erupts-after-wisconsin-police-shoot-black-man/6385663/ | work = [[KABC-TV|ABC7]] | publisher = Associated Press |accessdate=2020-08-24}}</ref>另一名证人说，警察赶到时，布莱克正在两名互相吵架的女子之间协调。<ref name=PeiserWP/>警察工会指出，警察的出警原因是布莱克试图偷取被报警人的车与车钥匙。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|last=Richmond|first=Todd|date=2020-08-28|title=Kenosha police union gives its version of Blake shooting|url=https://apnews.com/48c70ebf843f6018d66bddd4e5112e6f|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-08-29|website=[[Associated_Press|AP]] NEWS}}</ref>

在现场，警方试图制服布莱克，其中两名警察对布莱克使用了[[电击枪|电击枪]]。<ref name="officertry">{{cite news | date = 2020-08-28 | title = 2 Police Officers Tried To Stop Jacob Blake With Stun Guns: Wisconsin Justice Department | url = https://www.cbc.ca/news/world/jacob-blake-police-kenosha-wisconsin-1.5703414 | work = CBC News}}</ref><ref name=PeiserWP/><ref name="npr"/>一名路人在现场录制了影片，他对记者说自己听到警察大喊“放下刀”，但“并没有看见他手中有任何武器，他并没有使用暴力”。<ref>{{cite news | last = Pramuk | first = Jacob | date = August 24, 2020 | title = Joe Biden Says Kenosha Cops must be held accountable' for shooting Black man Jacob Blake in the back | url = https://www.cnbc.com/2020/08/24/jacob-blake-joe-biden-calls-for-probe-of-kenosha-police-shooting.html | work = [[CNBC|CNBC]] |accessdate=2020-08-24}}</ref>警察工会称，布莱克当时左手持刀，但警察一开始并没有注意到他手中的武器，而布莱克“与警察大打出手，一名警察被夹头”，不听从警察将刀子放下的要求。<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|last=Eligon|first=John|last2=Mervosh|first2=Sarah|last3=Jr|first3=Richard A. Oppel|date=2020-08-28|title=Jacob Blake Was Shackled in Hospital Bed After Police Shot Him|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/28/us/jacob-blake-shackles-assault.html|access-date=2020-08-29|issn=0362-4331}}</ref>“由于与布莱克无法用口头交流，物理阻拦等不太致死的方式也不奏效，警察不得不掏出武器”，警察工会进一步补充。<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|last=Schaper|first=David|date=2020-08-28|title=Police Union In Kenosha, Wis., Provides Account Of Jacob Blake Shooting|url=https://www.npr.org/sections/live-updates-protests-for-racial-justice/2020/08/28/907316697/police-union-in-kenosha-wis-provide-account-of-jacob-blake-shooting|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-08-29|website=[[National_Public_Radio|NPR]] |language=en}}</ref>布莱克的一名律师对此表示反对，称这一举措过于“夸张”，认为警察才是暴力的一方，一抵达现场就开始对布莱克动手了。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Chavez|first=Nicole|last2=Sanchez|first2=Ray|last3=Andone|first3=Dakin|date=August 28, 2020|title=Jacob Blake attorneys deny police union allegations of fight with officers before shooting|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/08/28/us/jacob-blake-wisconsin-friday/index.html|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-08-29|website=[[CNN|CNN]]}}</ref>在扭打完后，布莱克回到其车辆驾驶员一侧，拉斯滕·谢斯基和另一名警察用手枪指着他紧随其后。谢斯基试图用手抓住布莱克，但布莱克打开车门径直侧身进入车身，随后谢斯基抓着布莱克，从背后向他开了七枪。<ref name=PeiserWP/><ref>{{cite news |last=Flores |first=Terry |date=August 23, 2020 |title=WATCH NOW: State DOJ Will Probe Officer-Involved Shooting; Man In Serious Condition |url=https://www.kenoshanews.com/news/local/watch-now-neighbors-man-shot-by-police-at-40th-street-and-28th-ave/article_f1adbd13-3a15-5cdd-bd4e-95113ca36de4.html |work=Kenosha News |accessdate=2020-08-24}}</ref>2020年8月26日的媒体发布会上，威斯康星州司法部长{{tsl|en|Josh Kaul|乔什·考尔}}称，在布莱克车中驾驶室车底板上发现了一把刀。考尔亦表明，布莱克曾告知探员自己有刀，但考尔并未描述刀的具体样式，亦未告知这把刀是否与枪击有关。布莱克的律师否认了布莱克持刀的说法。<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Mcdermid | first1 = Brendan | last2 = Maturen | first2 = Stephen | date = August 27, 2020 | title = New Details in Police Shooting of Jacob Blake: A knife Was Found at the Scene | url = https://nationalpost.com/news/world/wisconsin-investigators-say-knife-found-at-scene-of-police-shooting-of-jacob-blake-2 | work = National Post}}</ref>

布莱克随后被紧急送至威斯康星州[[沃瓦托萨|沃瓦托萨]]的Froedtert医院。<ref name="npr">{{cite news|url=https://www.npr.org/2020/08/24/905316709/wisconsin-police-shooting-leaves-black-man-in-serious-condition |title=Wisconsin Police Shooting Leaves Black Man In 'Serious Condition' |date=2020-08-24 |website=[[NPR|NPR]] |first=Emma |last=Bowman |accessdate=2020-08-24}}</ref>其父在8月25日宣布布莱克腰部以下瘫痪，医生尚不清楚是否会造成终身瘫痪。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/2020/8/25/21400481/jacob-blake-kenosha-police-shooting-riots-evanston |title=Jacob Blake's father says son's paralyzed from waist down after police shooting in Kenosha |date=2020-08-24 |first=Clare |last=Proctor |website=[[Chicago_Sun-Times|Chicago Sun-Times]]}}</ref>此外，布莱克手臂中枪，胃、肾、肝亦受损，不得不摘除其大部分小肠和[[结肠|结肠]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/08/25/us/jacob-blake-kenosha-wisconsin-protests/index.html |title=Jacob Blake needs 'a miracle' to walk again after Kenosha police shot him, attorney says |last1=Chavez |first1=Nicole |last2=McLaughlin |first2=Eliott C.  |last3=Maxouris |first3=Christina |date=2020-08-25 |website=CNN |access-date=2020-08-27}}</ref>因逮捕令的关系，布莱克最开始被两名警察拷着手铐押送到医院，直到其开始上绷带了才解开。<ref>{{cite news | last = Kates | first = Graham | date = 2020-08-28 | title = Jacob Blake no longer handcuffed to his hospital bed, attorney says | url = https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/crime/jacob-blake-is-being-secured-with-restraints-to-his-hospital-bed/ar-BB18ty4E?li=BBnb7Kz | work = CBS News}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Bellware |first1=Kim |last2=Craig |first2=Tim |last3=Berman |first3=Mark |last4=Witte |first4=Griff |title=In Kenosha, Jacob Blake’s shooting deepens longstanding resentments and fears |date=2020-08-28 |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/national/jacob-blake-is-no-longer-handcuffed-in-wisconsin-hospital-attorney-says/2020/08/28/3b188454-e953-11ea-bc79-834454439a44_story.html |work=Washington Post}}</ref>

